<div class="not-content grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 my-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <!-- Model Description -->
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The 'Pilot to Scale' Model</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
        We don't believe in locking you into massive contracts before proving value. Our model is built on trust and measurable results.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-600/20 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 font-bold border border-indigo-500/30">1</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg">The Pilot (90 Days)</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mt-1">Low-risk entry. We implement the core infrastructure and launch initial acquisition campaigns. The goal is to establish a baseline Cost Per Lead (CPL).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-600/20 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 font-bold border border-purple-500/30">2</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Optimization</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mt-1">Once data is flowing, we deploy AI agents to refine lead qualification, ensuring your sales team only speaks to prospects ready to buy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-600/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 font-bold border border-emerald-500/30">3</div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-lg">Scale</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 mt-1">With unit economics proven, we uncork the budget. You scale revenue, not headcount.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Metric Card (Glowing) -->
  <div class="relative">
    <!-- Glow Effect -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-500 rounded-3xl blur-2xl opacity-20 -z-10 transform rotate-3 scale-105"></div>
    
    <div class="glass-panel rounded-3xl p-10 text-center relative border border-indigo-500/30">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest shadow-lg mb-8">
        Primary Metric
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mb-2">We Optimize For</h3>
        <div class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6">
        Qualified<br/>
        <span class="text-gradient">Appointment</span>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-xs mx-auto text-sm mb-8">
        Vanity metrics like "clicks" or "impressions" don't pay the bills. We focus on getting the right people on the calendar.
        </p>
        
        <a href="/audit" class="inline-block w-full py-4 rounded-xl bg-white text-indigo-950 font-bold hover:bg-gray-100 transition shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5">
        Start Your Pilot
        </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>